## Phase 2 vs adjacent phases

| Defer (Phase 3+) | In scope (Phase 2) |
|------------------|-------------------|
| Responsive layout fixes | File splits & import layers |
| `objectives.css` dedupe | `import/no-cycle` enforcement |
| Screenshot visual regression | Break state↔logic↔services cycles |
| Console boot log redesign | `ui.js` feature modules |
| Version tag / 1.0 release | Largest JS file < 1,500 lines |

| Already done (Phase 0–1) | Do not redo |
|---------------------------|-------------|
| `npm test` CI gate | Re-litigate test exclusions |
| Deploy console strip | Move strip to source repo |
| Duplicate pause-heat test | Delete tests to hit line limit |

