## ESLint addition (exit criteria)

When ready, extend `config/eslint.config.js` `public/src` block:

```js
"import/no-cycle": ["error", { "maxDepth": 10, "ignoreExternal": true }]
```

Start with `"warn"`, fix all reported cycles, then promote to `"error"`.
